@base_url = http://localhost:5153

### Health Check - 检查API状态
GET {{base_url}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Health Check - 数据库连接测试
GET {{base_url}}/api/health/database-simple
Accept: application/json

### Debug - 查看连接配置
GET {{base_url}}/api/health/debug
Accept: application/json

###
### ===== 组织管理 API =====
###

### 获取所有组织 - Organizations List (支持分页)
GET {{base_url}}/api/organizations?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 获取所有组织 - 快速模式（推荐，避免COUNT查询）
GET {{base_url}}/api/organizations?page=1&pageSize=5&includeCount=false
Accept: application/json

### 获取单个组织详情 - Curtin Management and Marketing
# UUID: 87820689-13ac-48d9-b244-9badc5c35155 代表 "Curtin Management and Marketing"
GET {{base_url}}/api/organizations/87820689-13ac-48d9-b244-9badc5c35155
Accept: application/json

### 获取单个组织详情 - Test Organization  
# UUID: bd6f6592-a52c-4e17-a5c7-f241153a10c8 代表 "Test Organization"
GET {{base_url}}/api/organizations/bd6f6592-a52c-4e17-a5c7-f241153a10c8
Accept: application/json

### 创建新组织 - Create Organization
POST {{base_url}}/api/organizations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "新测试组织",
  "contactPerson": "张三",
  "contactPhone": "+61 555666777"
}

### 更新组织 - Update Curtin Management and Marketing
# 更新 UUID: 87820689-13ac-48d9-b244-9badc5c35155 的组织信息
PATCH {{base_url}}/api/organizations/87820689-13ac-48d9-b244-9badc5c35155
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactPerson": "新的联系人",
  "contactPhone": "+61 888999000"
}

### 软删除组织 - Soft Delete Test Organization
# 删除 UUID: bd6f6592-a52c-4e17-a5c7-f241153a10c8 (设置 isActive = false)
DELETE {{base_url}}/api/organizations/bd6f6592-a52c-4e17-a5c7-f241153a10c8